{"tid":1342520,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"全部人同我向屋企人做文宣！！","createTime":"2019-07-21T17:40:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T17:40:32.000Z","uid":104808,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8f678f16fb58975f363304928726b6e1d269c3f9","tid":1342520,"uid":104808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:40:16.000Z","msg":"一直都做緊cd rom<br />\n淨係識幫手推post同出尼遊行:(<br />\n但見到元朗警黑合作得咁完美 <br />\n真係好嬲好嬲好嬲好嬲好嬲！<br />\n忍唔住出post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知好多人呢兩個月都唔敢同屋企講太多政治<br />\n但聽日你一 定 要 講！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（1）平時譴責暴力 要守護香港既<br />\n 叫佢mak大對眼 去睇清楚 <br />\n班白衫係幾咁痴線<br />\n拎曬木棍同開心刀 見人就打 <br />\n唔止黑衫示威者<br />\n男女老幼普通市民<br />\n無一倖免<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（2）支持香港警察既 叫佢睇清楚<br />\n班黑警係點樣見到白衫就調轉頭走<br />\n同埋白衫走警察到個時機係幾咁完美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（3）支持建制既 叫佢睇清楚<br />\n何君堯點樣同白衫握手 影相比手指公！<br />\n官黑勾結呀！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有佢地講既論點 今晚全部崩塌曬！<br />\n跟本站唔住腳！<br />\n以後佢地再講示威者點點點<br />\n拎番呢條片 駁番佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後如果睇曬之後 兩老都係話打得好既話<br />\n咁RIP 你可以放棄同佢講道理<br />\n因為佢已經唔再願意 係唔願意分是非黑白！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全部都係立場個live有！<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/standnewshk/#!/story.php?story_fbid=407353793207073&amp;id=710476795704610\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2F%23%21%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D407353793207073%26id%3D710476795704610&d=Px13HBr2%2FanjjqouUL7W1KCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=23f09f6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/standnewshk/#!/story.php?story_fbid=407353793207073&amp;id=710476795704610</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好以為無用 屋企人先係你見得最多 最近 <br />\n最大機會做文宣既對象<br />\n加油呀 香港人！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02657f23ee84441d30072cccf921df226c24470a","tid":1342520,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:40:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}